  "detailed_description": "Arrog is an enigmatic puzzle adventure game featuring hand-drawn art and set in a bizarre black-and-white world with color accents. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1185700/extras/4eae397616745806ce103299a528a1c3.poster.avif?t=1729491414\" width=600 height=410 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1185700/extras/4eae397616745806ce103299a528a1c3.webm?t=1729491414\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1185700/extras/4eae397616745806ce103299a528a1c3.mp4?t=1729491414\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>A tale about the journey of a man accepting his death through his dreams.<br></li><li>A unique black-and-white art style and traditional animations used in a bizarre world.<br></li><li>An intense 30-minute narrative experience.<br></li><li>A hand-crafted soundtrack for each section of the game.</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "Arrog is an enigmatic puzzle adventure game featuring hand-drawn art and set in a bizarre black-and-white world with color accents. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1185700/extras/4eae397616745806ce103299a528a1c3.poster.avif?t=1729491414\" width=600 height=410 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1185700/extras/4eae397616745806ce103299a528a1c3.webm?t=1729491414\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1185700/extras/4eae397616745806ce103299a528a1c3.mp4?t=1729491414\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>A tale about the journey of a man accepting his death through his dreams.<br></li><li>A unique black-and-white art style and traditional animations used in a bizarre world.<br></li><li>An intense 30-minute narrative experience.<br></li><li>A hand-crafted soundtrack for each section of the game.</li></ul>",
